---
title: Sticky Peri Peri Chicken with Charred Corn Rice and Yoghurt
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sticky Peri Peri Chicken in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R16_W51_UK_QR13651-3_Main_low-3e50c5c9.jpg
